e puro, um verdadeiro homem de bem.\n\n[/su_expand]\n<h4>Trailer</h4>\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/fxzMCOsr4IM\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>', 'Osmosis', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '153-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-12-11 22:50:02', '2020-12-12 00:50:02', '', 153, 'http://localhost/minhalistanetflix/2020/12/11/153-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
